betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABZg.name=硅岩蜂
betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABZg.desc=一只硅岩蜂.它不能让你免做硅岩处理线,但如果你科技足够的话,可以用它的蜂窝来做个诱变机!

# Quest: Decaying
betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABZw.name=腐烂蜂
betterquesting.quest.AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAABZw.desc=腐烂蜂并不比前三种蜜蜂更有用.但现在应该清楚的是,我们离镥蜂不远了!

